Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 抱、抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但、但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那為什麼能進高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那、那是因為……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是跳級的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厲害啊 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說腦袋非常的聰明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為應付課業綽綽有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以上課才會睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 好耀眼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.53,0:02:28.00,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,480)\1c&H3A9EF7&}#05 據說這就是經產婦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:28.00,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,480)\3c&HF2C855&\bord8}#05 據說這就是經產婦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an1}但是依然是一個普通的高中生罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好啊 那明天的考試應該也很輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天的考…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}考試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我正打算準備考試真白就穿著睡衣鬧起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了 也好 考試什麼的小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是成績差會讓姐姐大人丟臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼這裡會出現紅緒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是當然的吧 姐姐大人在學校很有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她的妹妹要是成績差的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會給姐姐大人添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我覺得在這之前紅緒本人就有相當大的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家都應該清醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會添麻煩什麼的…那種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那種該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什、什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他一旦無法用語言來表達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就會用行動來表示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家裡寄信來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說了「下次派人來看看狀況」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還想來看看真白是不是真的能吃黏糊糊食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你已經能吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 啊啊 這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}未來有這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個還不能說是能吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒想到這麼快就會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那、那個 跟我也有關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對啊 比起我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅的事情更加重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是來看即將成為三峰家新娘的小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}料理  打掃  洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為一個…新…娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,540)\shad0\bord4\3c&H3D393C&\c&HFFD997&}成績沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,540)\shad0\bord4\3c&H3D393C&\c&H94F4FC&}家事萬能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,540)\shad0\bord4\3c&H3D393C&\c&HD2B6F9&}巨乳安產型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼特別的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以矛頭會先指向我這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以是誰會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道 可能是哪個親戚會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起裝的奇奇怪怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如讓他來看看平時的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以從今天開始真白碳的內衣就是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你連這個都買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種「平時」也可以讓別人看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了 還有其他什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天的考試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}考試結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白 中午囉 去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 今天去學生食堂看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你沒去過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}偶爾也吃點熱的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生食堂
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an7\fs35\fad(100,0)}本週推薦！！ \N黏稠蓋飯 \N納豆+秋葵+山藥 \N魚子+海帶莖+生雞蛋
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 家裡人要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊～ 畢竟立場是新娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是那樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為來客人的話就要做些準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果要住的話就要準備房間還有準備餐點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}配合來客的年齡準備和食或者西餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}點心也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}不用那麼操心也行啦…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然總是滿口抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅你其實已經默許了吧 白夜同學的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 不…那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好玩不好玩一點也不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你問什麼東西不好玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其是吐槽不能的這傢伙啊這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}光是救命恩人這一點就已經很狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是未婚夫什麼的是要怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}漫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本來是那麼黏姐姐的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懲罰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這就是讓小紅受傷的我的懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她只是正常的長大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然我很感謝白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我才是她最親近的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果想談戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找我不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒你能做到的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}與其說是戀愛 不如說是變態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的話那樣也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜你吃的是烏龍麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像都沒怎麼動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅做的更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被馴服了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}馴服？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總 總之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先想準備接待的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是準備齊全比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}克服納豆的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從接觸開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從這裡開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說你穿成這樣會著涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會 難得收到的 不穿就浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過 還是第一次穿這麼鮮豔的內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心情有點複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你喜歡啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過 從三峰家過來的人會是什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母親大人和姐姐大人都很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和她們相比 會怎麼看待我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在啊 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什 什…所以說要幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐也在呢 小紅碳
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…一町目的夜之森家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡是 幾町目來著
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之 先做好不管客人什麼時候到都能迎接的準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然可以做燒烤點心一類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但接待客人的話還是從商店買比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 白夜也來買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白託我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾納豆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是為了習慣納豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蜂蜜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就換煉乳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了 我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是迷路走到完全不相干的地方了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體不由自主的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好吃 城裡的誘惑實在多到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在蘋果很便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以做蘋果派了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 肉桂好像沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去買一下 你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了 你應該不知道是什麼樣的肉桂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是條狀 是粉狀不加糖的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Goo、Google一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯…我知道了你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡是三町目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能找到二町目的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就到一町目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯嗯 沒問題的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}鯛魚燒
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}點心店
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}甜莓工廠
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一次次被誘惑打敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好險好險 還要買檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去買一下你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才 很正常的交談了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一…一町目怎麼走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沿著這條路…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我剛好也去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帶您過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}東西我幫您拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 這孩子是？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx6\fry6\fs30\shad0\frz18.151\c&H4F4976&\3c&HAAA0D7&\pos(821,554)}烤麵包
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛來這一帶的人都不容易找到路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢 每條路上的房子都差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和服～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是哪家的大小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}覺得您穿和服很合適 很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 那個 有點不適合穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 胸部的原因啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是叫做乾納豆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不也還是有納豆感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為納豆就是納豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請問你要去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不介意的話可以一起過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是一町目的夜之森家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 真的來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 你們兩個還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼是和小紅一起來的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 那個…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫我媽媽也可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}開玩笑的～
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}初次見面 我叫三峰白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜和真白受您照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪裡哪裡 伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}旅途勞頓辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下是小紅的姐姐紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您累了吧 來請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這就是經產婦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}啊啊啊 怎麼辦呢 居然來得這麼快 但是這樣也不能哭嗚 怎麼辦呢 怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}馬麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之先去倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅凍結中？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡作為姐姐的我要振作起來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能丟小紅的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇啊 我來做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是夜之森小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 嚇到你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛開始有想過你會不會就是小紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個我可以趁熱吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 媽媽今天在上班
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然來之前先打了招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個時候在車站附近見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為來到這裡還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後就迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是轉來轉去 猶豫來猶豫去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迷路了那麼久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}經過一番猶豫 把巧克力味奶黃味還有原味的所有種類都買下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}於是 你是來做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫媽媽的真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是給真白的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你現在可以吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}信上是這樣寫著的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 加油 加油 一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 還是吃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 撒些無聊的謊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然自己想著有還是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明顯可以有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說回來 小紅真的長大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明那時候那麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 讓我摸一摸行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}超級重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沉甸甸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅這麼可愛的妹子是我家的兒媳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 可能是有點太急了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}將來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們一族人也少了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很難找到對象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看 因為開發什麼的住的地方也越來越少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也嚐嚐這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且 白夜為了救小紅用了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啦 這個也很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係哦 我也會給真白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家也請嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那一類的話題還沒告訴小紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們不是人類的事情也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汪汪好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他叫做白夜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和牠做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黑呼呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可愛啊 好孩子好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也默默在想是不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白的高中生幼女體型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有看到媽媽的蘿莉婆婆體型…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊不對 看到媽媽年輕的身材就一目了然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兩位是妖精啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是並不是大家都很小很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且白夜長得很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然不是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人們對我們有許多稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}魔物 怪物 鬼 幽靈……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 還有「我老婆」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這稱呼倒還是第一次聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是當然 突然聽到這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快點躺下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能走到房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我抱你去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 白夜也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發燒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暈暈的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想起來…什麼東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 退熱貼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 可能是事情發生得太突然 嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如 岳母是蘿莉什麼的很少見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然這話不該我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被嚇到的不是那以外的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 媽媽我喋喋不休的說了多餘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明大家不像紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一顆鋼鐵的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}承蒙誇獎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且這種事一般人不會說「啊 是這樣嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後相信的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊呀 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看我就是那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心靈美 坦誠的 童心未泯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}純潔的少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這種話是怎麼能冠冕堂皇的說出來的啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能是我的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 果然是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受傷的時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的很危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以白夜一著急 把自己一半的力量給了小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是因為是人類以外的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能有時身體還是會不適應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}休息一下就能好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 一直都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說…說了……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啦啦 不好意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽又多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們的事對大家要保密的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否則我們就沒有立足之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 我明白了 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜託你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是平時說了別人也不信呢 肯定會被說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「什麼 難道你腦內設定是這樣的嗎」 之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅也病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也差不多該告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個 也要乖乖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}注意身體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黏呼呼的 要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}腦內保存 腦內保存
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 小紅醬也要多保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為啥來的時候坐的是一般交通工具咧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為喜歡啊 坐車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是那個外表用媽媽的口氣說話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}該怎麼形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種是什麼感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難得來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}住一晚就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳一定很想跟媽媽撒嬌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜他們不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是靠白夜的力量才得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是這種話實在不能相信……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 不信不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬以前摸過白夜的頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜很高興的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你跟他做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啦 討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會惹白夜生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}摸頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為自己很高興所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}認為摸別人 別人也會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊啊 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}行李也挺重的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要快點回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鎮上的居民們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚有剛出爐的菠蘿麵包移動販賣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等一下 等一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等我～
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}菠蘿麵包10個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甜甜圈15個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}by 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臉真厚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 就用小姑來填補吧
